<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 01:26:38 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>秋意再临</title><link>https://some.pics/69dee94a18d5a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;呼……🥶 感觉又回到了秋天！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Screenshot of iOS weather app showing 60 degrees F current temperature in Sunnyvale CA" height="2868" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jezlyn/69dee94a18d5a.png" width="1320"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jezlyn.some.pics"&gt;@jezlyn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 01:26:38 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>双猫翘尾双猫同眠</title><link>https://some.pics/69dedd66357e6</link><description>&lt;p&gt;有趣的是，最上面的两只猫都摆着尾巴翘起的姿势，而最下面的两只灰猫则以相同的姿势在睡觉。😺&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Screenshot from Neko Atsume 2 showing a cartoon style illustration of a cafe with a cat tree made of 3 circular shelves on alternating side of a curved pole sitting on a black rectangular base: a black and gray tabby and white and black spotted cat sitting on the top two tiers, both loading with their tails up. A plain gray and a gray striped tabby cat are laying on the next lower tiers, both curled up sleeping in the same pose. Next to the cat tree is a wooden mat with a white and red-brown cat who is also curled up sleeping. " height="2868" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jezlyn/69dedd66357e6.png" width="1320"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jezlyn.some.pics"&gt;@jezlyn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 00:35:52 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>轻触</title><link>https://some.pics/69de9f1b450fa</link><description>&lt;p&gt;轻轻触碰&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Two empty black folding chairs stand next to each other, their front legs crossing slightly. The floor glows red with headlights that illuminate a stage further ahead" height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/69de9f1b450fa.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 20:10:06 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Rust编程语言</title><link>https://some.pics/69de54191586f</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Rust。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A closeup look of an old railing. Rusty. An an East Modernist facade in the back. " height="4184" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/69de54191586f.jpg" width="2355"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 14:50:03 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>困惑表情</title><link>https://some.pics/69de41afedefd</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🤷🏻‍♂️&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="🤷🏻‍♂️" height="3940" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/atog/69de41afedefd.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://atog.some.pics"&gt;@atog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 13:31:33 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>